{"tid":646920,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國旅行6日5夜求酒店推介","createTime":"2018-04-29T12:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T03:50:53.000Z","uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2e34de24c61c81a00b822ce6aaa23a404ca9c4b7","tid":646920,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:34:19.000Z","msg":"小弟同女女諗住5月尾去泰國輕鬆下，想搵間抵住嘅酒店，希望係住得舒服，如果有渡假feel就更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想走黎走去，主要想嘆下輕鬆下，所以諗住一間住哂5晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求巴打推介，筆直唔多，7百左右或以下一晚，當然愈抵愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01d195564be6e343129e40a6567f9fad8112b06","tid":646920,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"另外，聽聞蘇梅好靚，唔知有冇抵玩酒店，求推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9eb7f2fbfb6f745c919aed4548d158c0bd508cb","tid":646920,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T13:09:39.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc23d27ad13634dc6caca514ffec62f459d6608","tid":646920,"uid":125237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T13:29:07.000Z","msg":"不如住民宿<br />\n上airbnb睇"},{"pid":"e547e97fa7c2a598ddc85c7785fb118d5d376bbc","tid":646920,"uid":16990,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T13:30:34.000Z","msg":"伸手黨都起馬講下去泰國邊度啦"},{"pid":"9fd4f80ac878fec6261e3af35ebf46a50853e61c","tid":646920,"uid":86157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T13:33:19.000Z","msg":"X2 Vibe Bangkok Sukhumvit Hotel<br />\n曼谷bts on nut站，應該都平既不過有啲遠，我去兩次都係住喱間，隔離有細商場有food court有lotus"},{"pid":"a0395083ddcc78e1eb402ddd7c46da99a9ac4634","tid":646920,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote